  "detailed_description": "The Adventures of Poppe is a game where you will explore different locations and find various items that will come in handy throughout the game. They include, for example: a nut, a key, a toy hobby motor, miniature wire cutters etc. It will be your task to find out where and how to use these items.<br>By the way, Poppe is quite tiny. He's only a couple of inches tall. So any cockroach or even a fly can pose a mortal danger to him.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1941740/extras/8311c2c6ce1ecbe9e496828d9d7be038.poster.avif?t=1689072739\" width=780 height=392 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1941740/extras/8311c2c6ce1ecbe9e496828d9d7be038.webm?t=1689072739\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1941740/extras/8311c2c6ce1ecbe9e496828d9d7be038.mp4?t=1689072739\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Explore locations and collect items<br></li><li> Tailor your tactics to fight your way against enemies<br></li><li> Get upgrades and new abilities<br></li><li> Help out different NPCs to get their support in the future<br></li><li> Defeat bosses using your skills</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "The Adventures of Poppe is a game where you will explore different locations and find various items that will come in handy throughout the game. They include, for example: a nut, a key, a toy hobby motor, miniature wire cutters etc. It will be your task to find out where and how to use these items.<br>By the way, Poppe is quite tiny. He's only a couple of inches tall. So any cockroach or even a fly can pose a mortal danger to him.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1941740/extras/8311c2c6ce1ecbe9e496828d9d7be038.poster.avif?t=1689072739\" width=780 height=392 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1941740/extras/8311c2c6ce1ecbe9e496828d9d7be038.webm?t=1689072739\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1941740/extras/8311c2c6ce1ecbe9e496828d9d7be038.mp4?t=1689072739\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Explore locations and collect items<br></li><li> Tailor your tactics to fight your way against enemies<br></li><li> Get upgrades and new abilities<br></li><li> Help out different NPCs to get their support in the future<br></li><li> Defeat bosses using your skills</li></ul>",
